column16: Rougned Odor grounds out, third baseman Carlos Sanchez to first baseman Jose Abreu.
Bobby Wilson lines out to left fielder Melky Cabrera.
Bryan Holaday doubles (2) on a ground ball to left fielder Melky Cabrera, deflected by third baseman Todd Frazier.   Elvis Andrus to 3rd.
Elvis Andrus singles on a line drive to left fielder Melky Cabrera.
Ryan Rua strikes out on a foul tip.
Danny Santana grounds out, second baseman Brett Lawrie to first baseman Jose Abreu.
Eddie Rosario lines into an unassisted double play, first baseman Jose Abreu.   Kurt Suzuki doubled off 1st.
